# public/screenshots/ and public/og.png are mirrored from /screenshots at
# the repo root by scripts/sync-screenshots.mjs (runs on predev/prebuild).
# They ARE committed so Vercel builds with Root Directory=site work without
# needing the "Include source files outside Root Directory" toggle. Re-run
# `node scripts/sync-screenshots.mjs` after updating anything in /screenshots
# and commit the refreshed files alongside your other changes.
